        "content": "<p>You need to rename <code>Main.lean</code> into <code>General.lean</code>. I wrote up a little Lean 4 project template <a href=\"https://limperg.de/posts/2021-05-31-lean4-project.html\">here</a>; maybe you'll find that useful.</p>",
